      "title": "## Overview",
      "content": "This plan outlines the creation of a luxury wellness e-commerce website for SAANJH RITUALS, a premium Indian ritual tea brand. The site will blend high-end aesthetics with ancient Indian wellness, featuring a curated product catalog, brand story, and rich content sections."
