      "title": "## Key features",
      "content": "- **View Homepage Content**: Displays brand visuals, headlines, and calls to action.\n- **View Why Saanjh Information**: Presents core brand pillars (Ritual, Wellness, Origin) via icons.\n- **View Product Listing**: Showcases all luxury ritual tea blends with pricing and key benefits.\n- **View Product Details**: Provides in-depth information for each tea blend, including ingredients, descriptions, ritual instructions, and sourcing stories.\n- **Add to Cart**: Allows customers to add selected products to their shopping cart.\n- **View Brand Story**: Shares the brand's narrative with accompanying imagery and a call to action.\n- **View Ingredient Macro Gallery**: Displays high-quality macro shots of ingredients.\n- **View Evening Ritual Steps**: Outlines a step-by-step ritual process with illustrations.\n- **View Wellness Benefits Grid**: Highlights six key wellness benefits using bordered cards.\n- **View Testimonial Carousel**: Features customer testimonials, including video placeholders.\n- **View Sustainability & Origin Information**: Details the brand's commitment to sustainability and ethical sourcing.\n- **View Journal Articles**: Presents blog posts and articles related to wellness and rituals.\n- **Submit Email Capture**: Allows visitors to sign up for newsletters and receive ritual guides.\n- **View About Page Content**: Details the brand's origin, founder story, and philosophy.\n- **Submit Contact Form**: Enables visitors to send inquiries via a contact form.",
